N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 733.13 - Index of records

State Regulations

At each office of the public utility or municipality where
records are kept or stored, such records as are required by this Part to be
preserved shall be so arranged, filed and currently indexed that they may be
readily identified and made available to representatives of the
commission. Notes
